ypt, he, and his wife, and all that he had, and Lot with him, into the south.","year":-1918},{"id":"recs0QuQeFlXtXqC3","ref":"Gen.13.2","text":"And Abram was very rich in cattle, in silver, and in gold.","year":-1918},{"id":"recKIaY3a7awiLlgJ","ref":"Gen.13.3","text":"And he went on his journeys from the south even to Bethel, unto the place where his tent had been at the beginning, between Bethel and Hai;","year":-1918},{"id":"recMnriBbFkIZMlXE","ref":"Gen.13.4","text":"Unto the place of the altar, which he had made there at the first: and there Abram called on the name of the LORD.","year":-1918},{"id":"rec5Uwj0OlbqoLtUf","ref":"Gen.13.5","text":"And Lot also, which went with Abram, had flocks, and herds, and tents.","year":-1918},{"id":"recFljLk7Pssp6zfr","ref":"Gen.13.6","text":"And the land was not able to bear them, that they might dwell together: for their substance was great, so that they could not dwell together.","year":-1918},{"id":"recDzbeW3uuGmxrkq","ref":"Gen.13.7","text":"And there was a strife between the herdmen of Abram’s cattle and the herdmen of Lot’s cattle: and the Canaanite and the Perizzite dwelled then in the land.","year":-1918},{"id":"recSZEbh0HRymyYZu","ref":"Gen.13.8","text":"And Abram said unto Lot, Let there be no strife, I pray thee, between me and thee, and between my herdmen and thy herdmen; for we be brethren.","year":-1918}]}
